name: Clari-Not
details:
The Clari(not) is an Envelope controlled Vibrato/chorus/wow and flutter simulator, with the ability to modulate over an octave. 
It is available as a "Clean" 4-knob version or the "Fuzz" 5-knob version, which adds a Volume knob.
CONTROLS
Delay
Depth
Blend
Tracking
FEATURES
True Bypass
9V DC (negative tip)
